				<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><table class="infobox" cellspacing="3" style="border-spacing: 3px; width:22em;">
<tr>
<th colspan="2" class="hd" style="text-align:center; font-size:125%; font-weight:bold; background-color: orange">Kumbh Mela</th>
</tr>
<tr class="">
<td colspan="2" class="" style="text-align:center;"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Third_Shahi_Snan_in_Hari_Ki_Pauri.jpg" class="image" title="Kumbh Mela"><img alt="Kumbh Mela" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e4/Third_Shahi_Snan_in_Hari_Ki_Pauri.jpg/225px-Third_Shahi_Snan_in_Hari_Ki_Pauri.jpg" width="225" height="149" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e4/Third_Shahi_Snan_in_Hari_Ki_Pauri.jpg/338px-Third_Shahi_Snan_in_Hari_Ki_Pauri.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e4/Third_Shahi_Snan_in_Hari_Ki_Pauri.jpg/450px-Third_Shahi_Snan_in_Hari_Ki_Pauri.jpg 2x" /></a><br />
<span style="caption"><a href="Haridwar" title="Haridwar">Haridwar</a> Pilgrims gather at the third Shahi Snan in <a href="Har_ki_Pauri" title="Har ki Pauri">Har ki Pauri</a> to take the Royal Bath in <a href="Ganges_in_Hinduism" title="Ganges in Hinduism">Ganga</a> River, 2010.</span></td>
</tr>
<tr class="">
<th scope="row" style="text-align:left;">Official name</th>
<td class="" style="">Kumbh Mela, Maha Kumbha Mela</td>
</tr>
<tr class="">
<th scope="row" style="text-align:left;">Observed by</th>
<td class="" style=""><a href="Hindu" title="Hindu">Hindus</a></td>
</tr>
<tr class="">
<th scope="row" style="text-align:left;">Type</th>
<td class="" style="">Religious</td>
</tr>
<tr class="">
<th scope="row" style="text-align:left;">Begins</th>
<td class="" style=""><a href="Makar_Sankranti" title="Makar Sankranti">Makar Sankranti</a>, 14 January</td>
</tr>
<tr class="">
<th scope="row" style="text-align:left;">Ends</th>
<td class="" style=""><a href="Maha_Shivaratri" title="Maha Shivaratri">Maha Shivaratri</a></td>
</tr>
<tr class="">
<th scope="row" style="text-align:left;">2013 date</th>
<td class="" style="">14 Jan- 10 Mar <sup id="cite_ref-1" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-1"><span>[</span>1<span>]</span></a></sup></td>
</tr>
<tr class="">
<th scope="row" style="text-align:left;">Observances</th>
<td class="" style="">Shahi Snan (bathing for purification from sin)</td>
</tr>
</table>
